title: [fsx/p3d3]FSFX Packages
description:
FSFX Packages is a new way to simulate brand new effects around the different aircraft and sceneries under interesting environmental conditions. Since Microsoft Flight Simulator X doesn't come bundled with such realistic effects, we had to think out of the box to create this new sense of immersion. In addition to our generic package, and since every aircraft and scenery is different, we decided to develop addon-specific packages. This allows us to push the boundaries of what's never been seen before in terms of visual effects!

hapy flying
